# MeaChat Astro - Copilot Rules & Project Context

## Project Overview
You are working on **MeaChat** – a SaaS landing page built with **Astro + Tailwind CSS**.
- **Product**: Omnichannel messaging automation platform (WhatsApp, Instagram, Messenger bots).
- **Tech Stack**: Astro 5.x, Tailwind CSS 4.x, TypeScript, deployed on Cloudflare Workers.
- **Main App**: https://app.meachat.com (external SaaS dashboard; do NOT modify).
- **Repo Structure**:
  - `src/pages/` → Astro pages (routing)
  - `src/components/` → Reusable Astro components
  - `src/styles/` → Global CSS/Tailwind config
  - `public/` → Static assets (images, logos)

---

## Critical Project Rules

### 1. External Links & CTAs
- **ALL** login/signup/purchase buttons MUST link to: `https://app.meachat.com/login`
- This includes:
  - "Get started", "Start free", "Try now", "Login", "Sign in"
  - Plan selection buttons ("Choose plan", "Upgrade", "Start with Growth")
  - Add-on purchase buttons (Message Credits, AI Tokens)
- **NEVER** create auth flows or payment forms in this repo – they live in the main app.

### 2. Internationalization (i18n) & RTL
- **Supported locales**: English (`en`) and Arabic (`ar`)
- **Routes**:
  - `/` → English homepage
  - `/pricing` → English pricing page
  - `/ar` → Arabic homepage (RTL)
  - `/ar/pricing` → Arabic pricing page (RTL)
- **RTL Requirements for Arabic**:
  - Use `dir="rtl"` on `<html>` or layout wrapper
  - Flip layout direction: `flex-row-reverse`, `text-right`, etc.
  - Icons/arrows pointing left should mirror for RTL
  - Font: Keep English font for Latin text, Arabic font for Arabic script
- **Translation files** (if/when created):
  - `src/i18n/en.ts` – English strings
  - `src/i18n/ar.ts` – Arabic strings

### 3. Pages & Content Strategy
- **Homepage** (`/` and `/ar`):
  - Hero, features, use-cases, integrations, social proof, CTA
  - **DO NOT** include pricing tables, add-ons, or expert sections here
  - Strong CTA linking to `/pricing` or `/ar/pricing`
- **Pricing Page** (`/pricing` and `/ar/pricing`):
  - Plans grid (Starter / Growth / Enterprise – demo content)
  - Flexible Add-ons section (Message Credits + AI Tokens as recharge cards)
  - Expert/onboarding CTA section
  - FAQ (short, demo)
- **Legal Pages** (demo placeholders):
  - `/legal/privacy`, `/legal/terms`, `/legal/cookies`
  - `/ar/legal/privacy`, `/ar/legal/terms`, `/ar/legal/cookies`
  - Use placeholder text: "Demo content – final policy coming soon"

### 4. Design System & Styling
- **Brand Colors** (Tailwind config):
  - Primary: `#A78BFA` (violet/purple – `primary` in config)
  - Dark bg: `#060321`, `#151133`, `#241A4F` (nested sections)
  - Accent green (for AI/tokens): `#22C55E`, `#10B981`
  - Accent blue (for enterprise): `#0EA5E9`
- **Typography**:
  - Font family: System sans (or custom if defined in `@font-face`)
  - Headings: Bold, `text-3xl` to `text-4xl` on desktop
  - Body: `text-sm` to `text-base`, `text-gray-300`
- **Components Style**:
  - Rounded corners: `rounded-2xl` for cards, `rounded-full` for buttons
  - Borders: `border border-white/10` or `border-primary/60` for highlights
  - Shadows: `shadow-lg` for elevated cards
  - Buttons:
    - Primary: `bg-primary text-dark` (where `dark` is very dark purple/black)
    - Secondary: `bg-white text-dark` or outlined
    - Always `rounded-full` with `px-6 py-2.5` or similar padding

### 5. Add-ons Section (Critical Design Pattern)
- **Message Credits** and **AI Tokens** should display as **recharge cards** (like prepaid phone cards or gift cards).
- **Card Design**:
  - Horizontal layout, resembling a credit card or gift card.
  - **Top-left**: MeaChat logo or brand icon (e.g., `MC` for Message Credits, `MT` for AI Tokens).
  - **Top-right**: Package size and price (e.g., "100K messages", "$12").
  - **Bottom**: Short description or card code (e.g., "MC • MSG • 100K").
  - **Gradient backgrounds**:
    - Message Credits: violet/blue gradient (`from-[#4338CA] via-[#312E81] to-[#111827]`)
    - AI Tokens: green/teal gradient (`from-[#059669] via-[#065F46] to-[#020617]`)
  - **Border**: Subtle `border border-white/10` or `border-emerald-300/40` for tokens
  - **On Click**: Full card clickable or button inside linking to `https://app.meachat.com/login`
